<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Driving Simulator: Account Details</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f0f0f0; color: #333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px;">
                <img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D4E22AQHHVzazE2h93w/feedshare-shrink_800/0/1700209654860?e=1710374400&v=beta&t=lcavQKUnRBSI0FRSSinANjJiM5wH7bzKh_g3mjZrSHI" alt="Fellow Bot" style="width: 200px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 10px 20px; text-align: center;">
                <h2 style="color: #0275d8;">Hello {{name}}</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0;">Congratulations on successfully purchasing a ticket to our driving simulator.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0;">Your security is very important to us, so we prepared a password for you to ensure your session is not breached.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0;">Your password is <strong>{{password}}</strong>. Please use the email address you have provided in the payment details to log in.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0;">Alternatively if you are coming from a driving school, they will provide the email and password for you. You can ignore this message if that's the case.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
                Kind regards,<br>
                Toni From FellowBot
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5;">
                If you have any queries, please visit us on our website at https://www.fellow-bot.com and get in touch!
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
